	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idActorKilled, idActorKiller, S_EFFECTGROUP_SOUL_ATTRACTOR)
	Hydra.ActorFlagDynamicPrefabGroupForDespawn(idSelf)

end
